{"word":"ἀφνίδιος","slug":"ἀφνίδιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀφνίδιος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄφνω'><el>ἄφνω</el></a>\n<p/><i>unforeseen, sudden</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-ίως</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; also <el>-ιον</el>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/>"}]}